title: Fix Crash on Pause and Button Listeners Clicked
message:
Fix Crash on Pause and Button Listeners Clicked

Change implementation of Serializable to Parcelable which fixed crash when button listeners are clicked.
*When app is first paused and then resumed, serialization was not saving onclicklisteners. Changing to Parcelable saves them!
